data.description: Looking for a good investment property? Already generating $2500 a month? And with a whole unit ready to move in or rent out for at least $1300 more? This is the best property in Berrien Springs for house hacking, growing, or starting your real estate investing journey!  With a large yard and an oversized garage, SOLD DIRECTLY BY OWNER, this is the opportunity you were looking for. It is also close to town, convenient to local school and Andrews University campus, easy access to US-31 AND....the township park is behind your backyard giving you all the space you could want! The current owner moved to a different state and wants to move his investments there. You'll enjoy the beauty of a property that pays for itself and generates good returns. Ask today about this deal, or better yet, book your private showing soon!
